      "zh": "俱乐部一线队、成年国家队和 U 系列国家队主教练进入主统计；助教、顾问、技术总监和俱乐部青年队教练只作为履历线索。",
      "en": "First-team club, senior national-team, and youth national-team head coaches enter the primary sample. Assistants, advisers, technical directors, and club youth coaches remain reference-only."
